GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation> ;
    narr:childCount "6"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """The category began as 'curated expertise installation' (Strategy Doc V1), then narrowed: in Mar Scarlet [dropped 'curated'](narr:Claim_CuratedDroppedFromCategory), reasoning the installation itself implies curation, leaving the [definition](narr:Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise) as the layer above context engineering that governs not just what AI knows but how it thinks. From Apr the framing shifted axis — from mechanism toward product — [recast as goal-directed delegation with citable escalation](narr:Claim_CategoryExtensionDelegation), and by 24 Apr folded in [matching-search as the external deployment value](narr:Claim_CategoryExtensionMatchingSearch). By Apr 30 the [cross-vertical pattern](narr:Claim_CrossVerticalPattern) generalized the shape across architects, lawyers, therapists, advisors — but with non-additive compliance, hence healthcare cash-pay first. Most recently (May) [vetting reframed as beachhead, not destination](narr:Claim_VettingAsBeachhead): the wedge that creates a 'perspective primitive,' with configurable AI individuals as the larger frame.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryExtensionDelegation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryExtensionMatchingSearch> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CrossVerticalPattern> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CuratedDroppedFromCategory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_VettingAsBeachhead> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "expertise installation — the layer above context engineering that determines not just what AI knows, but how it thinks." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "never thought the curated part was particularly necessary." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "goal-directed delegation with citable escalation" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryExtensionDelegation> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "high-context expertise, low-cost-to-produce-perspective, high-cost-to-vet-via-conversation, asymmetric information" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CrossVerticalPattern> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Launch healthcare cash-pay first (cleanest regulatory)." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CrossVerticalPattern> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Vetting is not the destination; it is the wedge that creates the perspective primitive." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_VettingAsBeachhead> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The real product is creating a perspective that represents an individual." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_VettingAsBeachhead> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Two framings of the category coexist: 'expertise installation' as mechanism vs 'goal-directed delegation with citable escalation' as product — the latter supersedes but the mechanism framing still grounds the definition." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryExtensionDelegation> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryExtensionMatchingSearch> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Vetting is the explicit entry-point yet explicitly NOT the destination — the real product is the perspective primitive / configurable AI individuals, a much larger frame than the beachhead implies." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_VettingAsBeachhead> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Cross-vertical ambition (architects, lawyers, therapists, advisors) pulls against a deliberately narrow launch — therapy, insurance-billed care, and legal are deferred due to non-additive compliance risk." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CrossVerticalPattern> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Superseded framing someone may still reach for: 'curated expertise installation' from Strategy Document V1, dropped Mar 31." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CuratedDroppedFromCategory> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_CategoryDefinitionCuratedExpertise> ] ;
    narr:writer "claude (subscription)" .
}